<h3>Food products and agricultural produce from Canada.</h3>
<p style="margin-bottom:0px; text-transform:uppercase">Agricultural produce</p>
<p>We source and supply Canadian fruit and vegetable produce of the highest consumer quality and health standards: potatoes, carrots, onions, apples, pears and others.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0px; text-transform:uppercase">Maple syrup and maple products.</p>
<p>Sugar maple is an endemic species for the North American continent and is a national tree of Canada. Maple syrup, derived from its sap is a unique product with one-of-a-kind ensemble of more than 50 biologically active and antioxidant components, which are highly valuable diet-wise and crucially beneficial for people with diabetes, immune-related and inflammatory conditions.</p>
<p>COEC is an authorised dealer and representative of the biggest maple farmer and maple products manufacturer in Canada. This partnership allows us to offer mapley syrup and maple products at the most affordable prices.</p>

